# 🌟 **AI TradeGPT**  

> 🚀 Your AI-powered crypto trading assistant for seamless and secure trading.  

[![Visit Website](https://img.shields.io/badge/Visit-Website-blue?style=for-the-badge)](https://your-website-link.com)  
[![GitBook Documentation](https://img.shields.io/badge/View-GitBook_Docs-brightgreen?style=for-the-badge)](https://your-gitbook-link.com)  

---

## ✨ **Overview**  
AI TradeGPT is an advanced AI system designed to revolutionize the crypto trading experience. Built to simplify complex trading tasks, it offers:  

- **🚀 Token Launch:** Deploy tokens seamlessly on Pump.fun.  
- **📊 Token Info:** Get real-time data about tokens.  
- **💰 Trading Features:** Securely buy and sell tokens.  
- **🛡️ Security Checks:** Perform rug checks and avoid scams.  
- **📈 PnL Tracking:** Analyze profit & loss.  
- **🔄 SOL Transfers:** Easily transfer SOL to wallets.  
- **📂 Wallet Tracking:** Stay updated with wallet activities.  

---

## 🔥 **Features**  

| Feature                | Description                                                                                                                                              |
|------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| **Launch Token**       | Deploy your tokens seamlessly using Pump.fun.                                                                                                            |
| **Get Token Info**     | Retrieve detailed real-time information for informed decision-making.                                                                                    |
| **Buy & Sell**         | Conduct secure token transactions effortlessly.                                                                                                          |
| **Rug Check**          | Run advanced security checks to detect potential scams.                                                                                                 |
| **PnL Analysis**       | Track and analyze your profit and loss in real time.                                                                                                    |
| **Transfer SOL**       | Securely transfer SOL tokens between wallets.                                                                                                           |
| **Wallet Tracking**    | Monitor wallet holdings and track transactions with ease.                                                                                               |

